sources.title: Martian Land | Full Action Sci-Fi Movie
sources.description:
Martian Land - In the distant future, a large portion of humanity lives on Mars, in cities that resemble those once found on Earth. The cities are protected from the inhospitable Martian atmosphere by dome-like force-fields. When a massive sandstorm breaks through the dome and destroys Mars New York, those in Mars Los Angeles must figure out how to stop the storm before it wipes them out next.
2015.  Stars: Lane Townsend, Alan Pietruszewski, Jennifer Dorogi
